#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; is a &UML; diagram tool that can support you in the software "
"development process. Especially during the analysis and design phases of "
"this process, &umbrello; will help you to get a high quality product. &UML; "
"can also be used to document your software designs to help you and your "
"fellow developers."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; je &UML; orodje za diagrame, ki vam lahko pomaga pri procesu "
"razvoja programske opreme. Zlasti med fazo analize in načrtovanja tega "
"procesa je &umbrello; vam bo pomagal do visokokakovostnega izdelka. &UML; se "
"lahko uporablja tudi za dokumentiranje načrtov vaše programske opreme, da "
"pomaga vam in vašim kolegom razvijalcem."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Having a good model of your software is the best way to communicate with "
"other developers working on the project and with your customers. A good "
"model is extremely important for medium and big-size projects, but it is "
"also very useful for small ones. Even if you are working on a small one man "
"project you will benefit from a good model because it will give you an "
"overview that will help you code things right the first time."
msgstr ""
"Imeti dober model vaše programske opreme je najboljši način za komunikacijo "
"z drugimi razvijalci, ki delajo na projektu, in s svojimi strankami. Dober "
"model je izjemno pomemben za srednje in velike projekte, vendar je zelo "
"uporaben tudi za majhne. Tudi če delate na majhnem projektu enega človeka, "
"vam bo dober model koristil, saj vam bo dal pregled, ki vam bo pomagal "
"pravilno kodirati stvari že prvič."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UML; is the diagramming language used for describing such models. You can "
"represent your ideas in &UML; using different types of diagrams. &umbrello; "
"2.11 supports the following types:"
msgstr ""
"&UML; je diagramski jezik, ki se uporablja za opis takih modelov. Svoje "
"zamisli lahko predstavite v &UML; z uporabo različnih vrst diagramov. "
"&umbrello; 2.11 podpira naslednje vrste:"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram razreda"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sequence Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram zaporedja"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collaboration Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram sodelovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Case Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram primera uporabe"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "State Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram stanj"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activity Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram dejavnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Component Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram komponent"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deployment Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram razmestitve"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entity Relationship Diagram"
msgstr "Diagram odnosa entitet"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information about &UML; can be found at the website of <ulink url="
"\"http://www.omg.org\"><acronym>OMG</acronym>, http://www.omg.org</ulink> "
"who create the &UML; standard."
msgstr ""
"Več informacij o &UML; lahko najdete na spletnem mestu <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.omg.org\"><acronym>OMG</acronym>, http://www.omg.org</ulink>, ki "
"ustvarja &UML; standard."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We hope you enjoy &umbrello; and that it helps you create high quality "
"software. &umbrello; is Free Software and available at no cost, the only "
"thing we ask from you is to report any bugs, problems, or suggestions to the "
"&umbrello; developers at <email>umbrello-devel@kde.org</email> or <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Upamo, da vam je &umbrello; in da vam pomaga ustvariti visokokakovostno "
"programsko opremo. &umbrello; je prosta programska oprema in je na voljo "
"brezplačno, edina stvar, ki jo prosimo, je, da prijavite morebitne hrošče, "
"težave ali predloge &umbrello; razvijalci na <email>umbrello-devel@kde.org</"
"email> ali <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."
